data.description: Welcome to the Lake!  This is a great lake house if you are looking for privacy and serenity.  With 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths plus additional rooms for office, den, or more sleeping spaces.  This house would make for a great VRBO with the finished basement and additional rooms.  New stainless appliances in the kitchen.  Open living space and gorgeous wood floors make the common area cozy and comfortable.  Roof and systems are all in great shape.  There is a small neighborhood golf course across the road for entertainment when you aren't out of the lake.  Single boathouse includes boatlift and storage area.  You won't find a prettier view or better water in this price range.
